Her First — AI Chatbot for Puberty and Period Education

Overview
Her First is a chatbot designed to support girls who are experiencing puberty or getting their first period. It provides simple, clear, and friendly answers based on trusted educational content.
The goal of this project is to create a safe and accessible space where users can ask questions and better understand their bodies.

How it works
This project uses a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) approach.
A collection of educational documents related to puberty, menstruation, and hygiene is preloaded into the system. These documents are split into smaller chunks and converted into embeddings.
When a user asks a question: The system generates an embedding for the query. It retrieves the most relevant chunks from the database using similarity search. These chunks are passed to a language model to generate a response

Tech Stack: Python, FastAPI (backend API), FAISS (vector database for similarity search), OpenAI API (language model and embeddings), HTML, CSS, JavaScript (frontend UI)

How to run the project


Clone the repository
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd project-chatbot


Create a virtual environment
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate


Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt


Set your API key
setx OPENAI_API_KEY "your_api_key"


Restart the terminal after setting the key.


Run the server
uvicorn main:app --reload


Open the application
http://127.0.0.1:8000/



Disclaimer
This chatbot is for educational purposes only and does not replace professional medical advice.


